➜【星连文学社】江西诗人时差先生：灵魂深处
http://www.sohu.com/a/411099352_100115135	47072
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200802/c727ac3b5bb64e46b2dc3c2c401d9e5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灵魂深处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月已慢慢变老</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老得快要掉牙了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太阳还是那般的执着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵魂已遁入空门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会苏醒么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万物开始喧哗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好望角早已发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留下审判的结局</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">印第安人的眼泪呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有犹太人的悲歌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有音乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不见胜利的号子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有血与泪的历史</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大洋变得不平静</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无时无刻不在撞击难民的孤岛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陆地浮躁了</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
